# FDS Enterprise — CI/CD Pipeline Jenkins

## Stages de la pipeline

```
📥 Checkout
    ↓
🧪 Test (pytest + coverage)
    ↓
🔍 Code Quality (Flake8 + Safety) ← parallel
    ↓
🐳 Build Docker Image (multi-stage)
    ↓
🔒 Security Scan (Trivy)
    ↓
📤 Push Docker Hub
    ↓
🚀 Deploy (SSH → docker compose up)
    ↓
💨 Smoke Tests (/health, /metrics, /api/transactions)
```

## Structure attendue

```
fds-enterprise/
├── Jenkinsfile                ← Ce fichier
├── tests/
│   └── test_fds_enterprise.py ← Tests CI
├── backend/
│   ├── Dockerfile
│   ├── requirements.txt
│   ├── app.py
│   ├── config/settings.py
│   ├── models/
│   ├── routes/
│   ├── services/fraud_service.py
│   └── middleware/
├── nginx/nginx.conf
├── prometheus/prometheus.yml
├── grafana/provisioning/
├── docker-compose.yml
└── .env
```

## Credentials Jenkins à configurer

| ID Jenkins            | Type                      | Valeur |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|--------|
| `docker-hub-creds`    | Username/Password         | Login Docker Hub |
| `DOCKER_REGISTRY`     | Secret text               | Ton username Docker Hub |
| `DEPLOY_SERVER_IP`    | Secret text               | IP du serveur (ex: 51.xx.xx.xx) |
| `deploy-ssh-key`      | SSH Username + Private Key| Clé SSH vers le serveur |

## Plugins Jenkins requis

```
Pipeline, Git, SSH Agent, AnsiColor,
Cobertura, JUnit, Credentials Binding
```

## Installer Jenkins sur Ubuntu

```bash
curl -fsSL https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian/jenkins.io-2023.key | sudo tee \
  /usr/share/keyrings/jenkins-keyring.asc > /dev/null
echo deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/jenkins-keyring.asc] \
  https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian binary/ | sudo tee \
  /etc/apt/sources.list.d/jenkins.list > /dev/null
sudo apt update && sudo apt install jenkins docker.io -y
sudo usermod -aG docker jenkins
sudo systemctl start jenkins
```

## Créer la Pipeline dans Jenkins

1. **New Item** → Pipeline → OK
2. **General** → Discard old builds → Max 10
3. **Build Triggers** → Poll SCM → `H/5 * * * *` (toutes les 5 min)
4. **Pipeline** → Pipeline script from SCM → Git
5. **Repository URL** → `https://github.com/TON_USER/fds-enterprise`
6. **Script Path** → `Jenkinsfile`
7. **Save** → Build Now

## Lancer en local (test rapide)

```bash
# Sans PostgreSQL/Redis (SQLite pour les tests)
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt pytest pytest-flask
pytest ../tests/ -v
```

## Endpoints de smoke test

| Endpoint | Attendu | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `GET /health` | `{"status":"ok"}` | Santé app + DB + Redis |
| `GET /metrics` | Prometheus metrics | Monitoring |
| `GET /api/transactions` | `401` | Auth requise |
